Short: A fast backfill hook with datatype images
Type:  dev/gui
Uploader: walter@btm2x2.mat.uni-bayreuth.de (Walter Dörwald)
Author: walter@data.mayn.sub.de (Walter Dörwald)

This is an example of a backfill hook for screens that uses datatypes.library to load the images.
The hook uses a "picture cache" with an optimized blitting algorythm to speed up rendering.

This code is public domain, do with it what you like (e.g. writing good software ;))

Comments and suggestions are always welcome.
